metadata.name: Tigerist I
metadata.description:
Tigerist I is the first piece of an animal exclusive series.

When you are afraid, face your problem without fear, and you’ll get through it.

During this piece creation I’ve understood deeply that I have to live everyday as my last one.

1/1

The collector will receive the high quality animation too.

The tiger is with you, the power to face every problem is always inside you.
